            "text": " that the Transportation Department was ‚Äúconstrained by law on some areas of rail regulation (like the braking rule withdrawn by the Trump administration.‚Äù Now, the department is publicly indicating that it will seek new rules on high-hazard flammable trains and electronic brakes ‚Äî and pledging to more aggressively use its executive authority under current law. Better late than never ‚Äî though it will require constant pressure to ensure these promises become reality.",
